From 5268f06d931e71cbc52d4fdcefd07908471e9ee4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Emily Shih <emily@usemotion.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 11:56:28 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] fix(slack): Resolve campaign_name missing from messages, add
 test controls, and creative breakdown

- Fix campaign_name reading from actionConfig instead of triggerConfig in automation evaluator
- Add test setup dialog with channel override and sample data selection for Slack test messages
- Add CreativeBreakdown component showing top headlines, primary texts, and CTAs by conversions
- Integrate creative breakdown into dashboard and ads pages

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
